.TH YASH-EVENTSCTL 1 "July 2026" "yash-app-events 0.1.0"
.SH NAME
yash-eventsctl \- inspect and control yash-app-eventsd
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B yash-eventsctl
[--json] [--socket PATH] [--timeout-ms MS] COMMAND
.SH COMMANDS
version, status, state, shutdown, profile, events follow, capture, replay MANIFEST,
diagnostic plan, and diagnostic export.
.PP
Diagnostic export requires an exact total returned by diagnostic plan plus the
--privacy-reviewed flag. Selected --element-id crops require a frozen preview.
.SH EXIT STATUS
0 success; 3 connection; 4 protocol/RPC; 5 validation; 6 timeout; 7 replay regression.
.SH SEE ALSO
yash-app-eventsd(1)
